column3: Rate increases totaling 36 % over 3 months resulted in my canceling my account here .
They have coupons discount for first second and third time customers through their website
This particular location has a good check in deal .
No appointment on a Saturday afternoon and they managed to get me in and out in an hour .
Rodney and his crew gave us a great price and did the work so quick , literally , it was done before we knew it
Reception hung up on me multiple times and would not listen .
Jimmy really cares about his customers and his craft .
Great customer service , great food that is fresh and cooked to order .
The staff here were very pleasant even through the cancellation process , and seemed to realize that someone 's ending use of a unit did n't have to mean permanent loss of a customer .
